ould%20not%20let%20us%20approach.%20Then%20they%20sent%20us%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20where%20we%20had%20to%20show%20photos%20to%20confirm%20he%20had%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20man%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20the%20state%20for%20help%2C%20saying%20his%20brother%20was%20the%20family's%20primary%20earner.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20poor%20people...%20where%20will%20go%2C%20what%20will%20we%20do%3F%20My%20brother%20was%20responsible%20for%20us...%20he%20also%20left%20behind%20a%20wife%20and%20child.%20There%20should%20be%20an%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20distraught%20kin%20-%20whose%20nephew%2C%20Sachin%20Yadav%2C%20worked%20at%20the%20petrol%20station%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20family%20would%20have%20never%20sent%20the%2023-year-old%20to%20work%20there%20if%20told%20about%20the%20dispute%20behind%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20billboard.%20%26quot%3BMy%20brother's%20son...%20he%20was%20working%20there%20for%20two%20years.%20We%20found%20out%20only%20yesterday%20night%20that%20he%20had%20been%20crushed%20by%20the%20billboard.%20We%20rushed%20there%20but%20there%20was%20such%20a%20commotion%20that%20no%20one%20could%20tell%20us%20anything.%20Only%20at%204%20am%20we%20were%20told%20to%20go%20to%20the%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F792728q_sachin-yadav-mumbai-billboard-collapse-victim_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20Yadav%2C%2023%2C%20was%20one%20of%20those%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20billboard%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20family%20members%20have%20also%20questioned%20the%20state%20government's%20compensation%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20death%2C%20pointing%20out%20many%20of%20those%20who%20were%20crushed%20to%20death%20had%20young%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20cousin%20brother%20(who%20died)...%20his%20child%20has%20just%20given%20her%20Class%2010%20exam.%20Will%20Rs%205%20lakh%20be%20enough%20for%20her%20education%3F%20How%20will%20his%20family%20survive%20now%20on%20this%20amount%3F%20And%20even%20if%20they%20can%2C%20it%20will%20take%20five-six%20months%20for%20the%20money%20to%20come.%20What%20will%20they%20do%20till%20then%3F%20They%20must%20think%20about%20this...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E21%20Hours%20Later%2C%20Rescue%20Ops%20Continue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aftermath%20of%20the%20horrible%20incident%20-%20search%20and%20rescue%20ops%20to%20save%20more%20people%20and%2C%20possibly%2C%20recover%20more%20bodies%20-%20continued%20into%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%20more%20than%2021%20hours%20after%20the%20collapse.%20Rescue%20ops%20included%20teams%20from%20the%20NDRF%2C%20or%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%2C%20as%20well%20as%20earth-movers%20from%20the%20BMC%2C%20and%20teams%20of%20emergency%20medical%20personnel.%20Gas-cutters%20have%20also%20been%20deployed%2C%20but%20there%20are%20concerns%20over%20using%20these%2C%20given%20the%20accident%20site%20is%20a%20petrol%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDRF%20is%20using%20two%20cranes%20-%20each%20weighing%20500%20tons%20-%20to%20shift%20the%20metal%20debris%20and%20create%20tunnels%20into%20which%20rescue%20personnel%20can%20crawl%20and%20pull%20out%20those%20trapped%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPainful%2C%20Sad%20Incident%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Varanasi%20today%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-files-nomination-from-varanasi-after-praying-at-iconic-ghat-temple-5659484%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_bigstory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20filed%20his%20nomination%20papers%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20tragedy%20and%20has%20announced%20ex-gratia%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Varanasi%2C%20UP%3A%20On%20the%20Ghatkopar%20hoarding%20collapse%20incident%2C%20Maharashtra%20CM%20Eknath%20Shinde%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B%20It%20is%20a%20painful%20and%20sad%20incident%2C%20I%20myself%20visited%20the%20spot%20yesterday.%20The%20government%20will%20bear%20all%20the%20expenses%20of%20the%20people%20injured%20in%20this%20incident.%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPxcNiTjb2b%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPxcNiTjb2b%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1790295789119684965%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20painful%20and%20sad%20incident...%20I%20visited%20the%20spot%20yesterday.%20The%20government%20will%20bear%20all%20expenses%20of%20people%20injured.%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20compensation%20will%20be%20given%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20(and)%20strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20hoarding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20has%20also%20reacted.%20She%20posted%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20%26quot%3BNews%20of%20several%20casualties%20due%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20hoarding%20in%20Ghatkopar%20area%20of%20Mumbai%20is%20extremely%20sad.%20I%20express%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20bereaved%20families.%20I%20pray%20for%20the%20speedy%20recovery%20of%20the%20injured%20and%20wish%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOfficials'%20Blame%20Game%20Over%20Billboard%20Collapse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20hoarding%20collapse%20has%20also%20triggered%20(an%20entirely%20predictable)%20blame%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20has%20declared%20the%20billboard%20-%20a%20120%20X%20120%20foot%20structure%20reportedly%20in%20the%20Limca%20Book%20of%20Records%20-%20was%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%2C%20i.e.%2C%20it%20did%20not%20give%20the%20advertising%20agency%20permission%20to%20erect%20that%20and%20other%20such%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20according%20to%20officials%20cited%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20BMC%20limits%20billboard%20sizes%20to%2040%20x%2040%20foot%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20ordered%20action%20against%20all%20illegal%20hoardings%20in%20the%20city.%20We%20are%20starting%20today.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20this%20case%20(as)%20this%20hoarding%20did%20not%20have%20permission.%20A%20complaint%20was%20also%20received%20that%20some%20trees%20had%20been%20cut%20so%20this%20hoarding%20could%20be%20visible.%20We%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20this%20regard%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20BMC%20Commissioner%C2%A0Bhushan%20Gagrani%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fvideo-7-injured-some-feared-trapped-after-mumbai-dust-storm-uproots-billboard-5653884%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E14%20Dead%20After%20Huge%20Billboard%20Falls%20During%20Mumbai%20Dust%20Storm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ad%20agency%20-%20Ego%20Media%2C%20which%20built%20four%20hoardings%20-%20each%20100-150%20metres%20from%20the%20other%20-%20on%20land%20leased%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20to%20the%20Police%20Welfare%20Corporation%20-%20is%20understood%20have%20to%20received%20'permission'%20from%20the%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Railways).%20The%20land%20had%20initially%20been%20given%20to%20the%20Government%20Railway%20Police%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civic%20body%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20demanding%20the%20hoardings%20still%20standing%20be%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hoarding-collapse-deaths-rise-to-14-police-case-against-ad-agency-5658087%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMumbai%20Hoarding%20Collapse%20Kills%2014%2C%20Ad%20Agency%20Had%20No%20Civic%20Body%20Clearance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GRP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20pitched%20responsibility%20back%20to%20the%20civic%20body%2C%20saying%20it%20does%20not%20have%20the%20equipment%20to%20take%20the%20structures%20down%20and%20asked%20the%20BMC%20to%20act%20instead.%20An%20official%20said%20the%20hoardings%20will%20be%20razed%20but%20offered%20no%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20police%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20ad%20agency's%20owner%20-%20identified%20as%20Bhavesh%20Bhinde%20-%20and%20others%20on%20charges%20for%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715679540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fjbckvbio_mumbai-billboard_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-billboard-collapse-we-are-poor-people-day-after-billboard-tragedy-human-cost-highlighted-5660652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20the%20deadly%2