sofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrench-pm-says-violence-is-never-a-solution-after-new-caledonia-riots%2Famp_articleshow%2F110113295.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Teams%20For%203%20Spots%3A%20Complete%20IPL%202024%20Playoffs%20Scenario%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20for%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%2C%20(IPL)%202024%2C%20playoffs%20qualification%20has%20intensified%20with%20the%20marquee%20T20%20tournament%20heading%20towards%20its%20business%20end.%20With%20just%20seven%20games%20remaining%20in%20the%20league%20stage%20of%20IPL%202024%2C%20the%20two-time%20winners%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20became%20the%20first%20team%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20playoffs%20this%20season.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%2C%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%20and%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%20have%20already%20been%20eliminated%20from%20the%20playoffs%20race%20after%20their%20dismal%20campaigns%20in%20the%20ongoing%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20five%20other%20teams%20are%20still%20in%20contention%20to%20secure%20the%20remaining%20three%20spots%20for%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20note%2C%20we%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20scenarios%20with%20which%20all%20the%20teams%20remaining%20for%20IPL%202024%20playoffs%20contention%20can%20still%20qualify.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajasthan%20Royals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20losing%20their%20last%20three%20matches%2C%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20(RR)%20are%20the%20overwhelming%20favourites%20for%20a%20top-two%20finish%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20league%20stage.%20With%2016%20points%20from%2012%20games%2C%20the%20Royals%20are%20placed%20second%20in%20the%20standings%20with%20a%20net%20run-rate%20of%20%2B0.349.%20The%20Sanju%20Samson-led%20Royals%20are%20still%20scheduled%20to%20face%20Punjab%20Kings%20(May%2015)%20and%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(May%2019).%20They%20need%20to%20win%20at%20least%20one%20of%20their%20remaining%20games%20to%20qualify%20for%20playoffs.%20If%20the%20Royals%20win%20both%20matches%2C%20they%20will%20finish%20in%20the%20top%20two.%20However%2C%20if%20RR%20suffer%20defeat%20in%20both%20games%2C%20they%20are%20still%20expected%20to%20qualify%20due%20to%20a%20better%20NRR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayed%3A%2012%2C%20Points%3A%2016%2C%20NRR%3A%20%2B0.349%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20PBKS%20(H)%2C%20KKR%20(H)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChennai%20Super%20Kings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20champions%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20are%20placed%20third%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20standings.%20Led%20by%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%2C%20CSK%20have%20registered%20seven%20wins%20and%20six%20losses%20this%20season%20with%2014%20points%20on%20the%20board.%20The%20five-time%20IPL%20champions%20will%20take%20on%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20in%20their%20final%20game.%20To%20qualify%20for%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs%2C%20CSK%20only%20need%20to%20beat%20RCB%20at%20the%20M.Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20on%20May%2018.%20With%20a%20net%20run-rate%20of%20%2B0.528%2C%20CSK%20will%20finish%20in%20the%20top%20four%20with%20a%20win%20on%20Saturday.%20However%2C%20if%20they%20lose%2C%20CSK%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20don't%20go%20down%20by%20more%20than%2018%20runs%20or%20allow%20RCB%20to%20chase%20in%2018.1%20overs.%20CSK%20also%20need%20to%20hope%20SRH%20and%20LSH%20lose%20both%20their%20scheduled%20games.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20both%20CSK%20and%20RCB%20can%20still%20qualify%20with%2014%20points%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayed%3A%2013%2C%20Points%3A%2014%2C%20NRR%3A%20%2B0.528%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20RCB%20(A)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESunRisers%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunRisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20are%20one%20of%20the%20other%20contenders%20for%20a%20top-two%20finish%20this%20season.%20With%2014%20points%20from%2012%20games%2C%20SRH%20are%20placed%20fourth%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20standings%20with%20a%20net%20run-rate%20of%20%2B0.406.%20The%20Pat%20Cummins-led%20outfit%20is%20scheduled%20to%20play%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(May%2016)%20and%20Punjab%20Kings%20(May%2019)%20in%20their%20remaining%20two%20fixtures%20at%20their%20home%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Meanwhile%2C%20SRH%20need%20to%20win%20at%20least%20one%20of%20their%20pending%20games%20to%20book%20their%20spot%20in%20the%20playoffs.%20If%20they%20win%20both%20their%20matches%2C%20they%20could%20challenge%20KKR%20and%20RR%20to%20finish%20in%20the%20top%20two.%20However%2C%20if%20they%20lose%20both%20games%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20CSK%2C%20RCB%20or%20even%20LSG%20could%20finish%20above%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayed%3A%2012%2C%20Points%3A%2014%2C%20NRR%3A%20%2B0.406%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20GT%20(H)%2C%20PBKS%20(H)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20have%20made%20a%20sensational%20comeback%20in%20IPL%202024%20to%20remain%20in%20playoffs%20contention.%20After%20winning%20just%20one%20of%20their%20seven%20games%20in%20the%20first%20half%2C%20RCB%20are%20on%20a%20five-match%20winning%20streak%20to%20jump%20to%20fifth%20in%20the%20standings%20with%2012%20points%20from%2013%20games.%20In%20order%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20playoffs%2C%20RCB%20first%20need%20to%20win%20against%20CSK%20by%2018%20runs%20or%20chase%20in%2018.1%20overs%20on%20Saturday%20to%20ensure%20a%20better%20NRR%20than%20the%20defending%20champions.%20Even%20after%20a%20win%2C%20RCB%20will%20be%20dependent%20on%20other%20results%20to%20squeeze%20into%20the%20playoffs.%20Faf%20du%20Plessis'%20men%20need%20SRH%20to%20lose%20both%20their%20games.%20They%20also%20require%20LSG%20to%20go%20down%20in%20one%20of%20their%20remaining%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayed%3A%2013%2C%20Points%3A%2012%2C%20NRR%3A%20%2B0.387%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20CSK%20(H)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%20Capitals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Delhi%20Capitals%20still%20have%20a%20mathematical%20chance%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs%2C%20it's%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20Rishabh%20Pant's%20men%20will%20finish%20in%20the%20top%20four.%20With%20a%20net%20run-rate%20of%20-0.482%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20below%20CSK%2C%20SRH%20and%20RCB%2C%20the%20Capitals'%20IPL%202024%20campaign%20is%20almost%20done%20and%20dusted.%20For%20DC's%20miraculous%20entry%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs%2C%20they%20first%20need%20to%20beat%20LSG%20by%20a%20huge%20margin%20to%20improve%20their%20net%20run-rate.%20The%20Capitals%20also%20need%20SRH%20to%20lose%20both%20their%20forthcoming%20games%20by%20massive%20margins.%20DC%20will%20also%20require%20CSK%20to%20beat%20RCB%20and%20LSG%20to%20go%20down%20against%20MI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayed%3A%2013%2C%20Points%3A%2012%2C%20NRR%3A%20-0.482%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20matches%3A%20LSG%20(H)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucknow%20Super%20Giants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20are%20one%20of%20the%20other%20contenders%20to%20finish%20in%20the%20top%20four.%20Having%20accumulated%2012%20points%20from%2012%20matches%2C%20the%20KL%20Rahul-led%20side%20is%20placed%20seventh%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20standings.%20However%2C%20LSG%20are%20scheduled%20to%20play%20struggling%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(May%2014)%20and%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(May%2017)%20in%20their%20final%20two%20league%20games.%20For%20their%20qualification%20in%20the%20playoffs%2C%20LSG%20need%20to%20win%20both%20their%20upcoming%20matches%20due%20to%20their%20poor%20net%20run-rate%20of%20-0.769.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20need%20to%20win%20both%20games%20with%20huge%20margins%20to%20improve%20their%20NRR.%20Even%20if%20they%20manage%20to%20win%20both%20matches%2C%20they%20can%20still%20finish%20outside%20the%20top%20four%20if%20CSK%20and%20SRH%20end%20the%20league%20stage%20with%2016%20points%20