t%3BWe%20got%20the%20information%20that%20the%20presiding%20officer%20caught%20a%20minor%20girl%20casting%20her%20vote.%20They%20are%20not%20registering%20an%20FIR.%20They%20are%20free%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20on%20me%20but%20not%20on%20others.%20My%20FIR%20started%20from%20'Ram%20Baan'.%20I%20am%20getting%20FIRs%20in%20the%20form%20of%20medals%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Latha%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Telangana%3A%20On%20FIR%20registered%20against%20her%2C%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20Madhavi%20Latha%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20We%20got%20the%20information%20that%20presiding%20officer%20caught%20a%20minor%20girl%20casting%20her%20vote...%20They%20are%20not%20registering%20an%20FIR.%20They%20are%20free%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20on%20me%20but%20not%20on%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FijvGtXUUYB%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FijvGtXUUYB%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1790292397861257468%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%2035-year-old.%20Last%20month%2C%20a%20video%20of%20Ms%20Latha%20in%20which%20she%20was%20seen%20pretending%20to%20draw%20and%20fire%20an%20arrow%20while%20near%20a%20mosque%20drew%20widespread%20criticism.%20Later%2C%20she%20denied%20aiming%20for%20the%20mosque%20but%20issued%20a%20public%20apology%20nonetheless%20for%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20was%20on%20Monday%20seen%20in%20a%20video%20requesting%20burqa-clad%20women%20voters%20to%20reveal%20their%20faces%20for%20identification%20purposes.%20This%20action%20prompted%20authorities%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20her.%20Contesting%20from%20the%20Hyderabad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20she%20defended%20herself%20by%20saying%20that%20her%20actions%20were%20merely%20an%20attempt%20to%20ensure%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20alleging%20that%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20booths%20are%20compromised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20Ms%20Latha%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20compelled%20to%20intervene%20due%20to%20the%20alleged%20inaction%20of%20the%20female%20police%20officers%20present%20at%20the%20polling%20booth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20candidate.%20As%20per%20law%2C%20the%20candidate%20has%20the%20right%20to%20check%20the%20ID%20cards%20without%20the%20facemasks.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20man%2C%20I%20am%20a%20woman%20and%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20humbleness%2C%20I%20have%20only%20requested%20them%20-%20can%20I%20please%20see%20and%20verify%20with%20the%20ID%20cards%3F%20If%20somebody%20wants%20to%20make%20a%20big%20issue%20out%20of%20it%2C%20that%20means%20they%20are%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Latha%20is%20challenging%20four-time%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20AIMIM%20chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20and%20BRS%20pick%20Gaddam%20Srinivas%20Yadav.%20This%20marks%20the%20first%20time%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20a%20female%20candidate%20from%20the%20Hyderabad%20constituency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20three-way%20showdown%20between%20the%20incumbent%20Congress%2C%20the%20opposition%20BRS%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20featuring%20a%20total%20of%20525%20candidates.%20Key%20battlegrounds%20include%20Hyderabad%2C%20Secunderabad%2C%20Karim%20Nagar%2C%20and%20Chevella%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715678820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F202