e%20workers%20pulled%20out%20of%20a%20hiring%20process%20for%20jobs%20that%20required%20office%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20some%20CEOs%20adjust%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20long%20workers%20might%20be%20able%20to%20resist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcool-fancy-workspaces-employers-startups-coming-for-bland-offices-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheading%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrict-return-to-office-mandates-could-drive-away-top-workers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework-from-home%20holdouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20giving%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20poll%2C%2036%25%20of%20people%20seeking%20senior-level%20jobs%20said%20a%20return-to-office%20mandate%20factored%20into%20their%20decision%20to%20look%20for%20a%20new%20role%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0even%20if%20they%20had%20good%20reason%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20in%20three%20also%20said%20they'd%20walked%20away%20from%20a%20hiring%20process%20in%20the%20past%20year%20because%20the%20would-be%20employer%20required%20people%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recently%20released%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gartner.com%2Fen%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2024-05-09-one-third-execs-given-a-rto-mandate-plan-to-leave%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%20by%20research%20firm%20Gartner%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%2C%20conducted%20in%20January%20among%20nearly%203%2C000%20job%20seekers%2C%20echoed%20Gartner%20research%20from%20late%202023%20that%20found%20one%20in%20three%20execs%20faced%20with%20an%20RTO%20mandate%20planned%20to%20ditch%20their%20employer%20because%20of%20it.%20That%20earlier%20survey%20also%20found%20that%2019%25%20of%20non-exec%20workers%20would%20likewise%20quit%20if%20forced%20to%20pick%20up%20their%20commute%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20from%20both%20snapshots%20underscore%20that%20while%20many%20workers%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20even%20CEOs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0appear%20to%20have%20tapped%20out%20on%20the%20RTO%20fights%2C%20there%20is%20still%20a%20segment%20of%20people%20unwilling%20to%20give%20up%20video%20meetings%20and%20at-home%20lunches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20as%20the%20market%20for%20white-collar%20jobs%20appears%20to%20be%20slowing%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20long%20workers%20can%20ghost%20their%20cubicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22032a06f9-36d0-438d-9225-1943ac7ad45e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'They%20still%20would%20leave'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECaroline%20Ogawa%2C%20a%20director%20in%20the%20HR%20practice%20at%20Gartner%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20findings%20showed%20how%20even%20when%20execs%20understood%20why%20the%20big%20boss%20would%20want%20them%20back%20in%20the%20office%2C%20that%20rationale%20wasn't%20necessarily%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20overwhelmingly%20felt%20like%20the%20organization%20provided%20a%20convincing%20reason%26quot%3B%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20still%20would%20leave%20if%20they%20were%20asked%26quot%3B%20to%20come%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOgawa%20said%20the%20findings%20were%20also%20notable%20because%20high-up%20executives%20are%20often%20the%20people%20tasked%20with%20implementing%20RTO%20mandates.%20However%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20what%20%3Cem%3Ethey%3C%2Fem%3E%20want%2C%20some%20still%20desire%20autonomy%20about%20where%20they%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOften%2C%20they're%20the%20ones%20kind%20of%20holding%20the%20bag%20for%20those%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20own%20actions%20in%20the%20job%20market%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20behaving%20like%20you%20would%20expect%20all%20candidates%20to%20behave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20workers%2C%20that%20behavior%20is%20wanting%20to%20retain%20the%20choice%20they%20had%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%20during%20the%20Great%20Resignation%20and%20believing%20they%20still%20have%20the%20upper%20hand%20over%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOgawa%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20it%20appears%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-slump-professional-white-collar-jobs-recession-high-salary-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20white-collar%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20slipping%2C%20many%20desk%20workers%20want%20to%20retain%20agency%20and%20call%20the%20shots%20about%20where%20and%20when%20they%20do%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230657cb5-4ee0-4781-a9d0-50af5b784365%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHybrid%20is%20here%20to%20stay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20CEOs%20appear%20to%20be%20hearing%20workers.%20In%20a%20recent%20survey%20by%20KMPG%20US%2C%20just%2034%25%20of%20US%20CEOs%20of%20large%20companies%20said%20they%20expect%20their%20people%20will%20be%20back%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-work-here-to-stay-ceos-rto-remote-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffice%20five%20days%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20next%20three%20years.%20That's%20a%20big%20drop%20from%20a%20prior%20survey%20in%202023%2C%20when%2062%25%20of%20CEOs%20held%20that%20expectation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHybrid%20is%20likely%20here%20to%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Knopp%2C%20chair%20and%20CEO%20at%20KPMG%20US%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20workers%20who%20want%20to%20log%20on%20from%20home%20are%20doing%20so.%20Erik%20Bernard%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20who%20works%20in%20IT%20in%20Australia%2C%20chose%20a%20higher-paying%20government%20job%20over%20a%20less%20lucrative%20role%20where%20he%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-chose-higher-paid-job-versus-working-from-home-unsure-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20from%20home%20most%20days%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%2C%20he%20recently%20told%20BI%20that%20he's%20not%20sure%20he%20made%20the%20right%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20he%20gets%20to%20work%20from%20home%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20avoid%20the%20hourlong%20drive%20to%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0he%20says%20he%20can%20get%20more%20sleep%20and%20time%20at%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20quality%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f726c62f-da11-4947-ad07-62e8089c9f61%5C%22%3EWhat's%20at%20stake%20with%20RTO%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGartner's%20Ogawa%20said%20now%20that%20we've%20had%20a%20few%20years%20of%20hybrid%20setups%20and%20other%20work%20arrangements%2C%20it's%20becoming%20clearer%20for%20companies%20and%20workers%20what%20the%20stakes%20are%20around%20RTO%20pushes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20companies%20will%20have%20to%20ask%20whether%20perceived%20benefits%20from%20priorities%20such%20as%20collaboration%20or%20innovation%20will%20outweigh%20the%20risks%20of%20potentially%20losing%20some%20workers%20who%20are%20firm%20about%20not%20making%20the%20trek%20to%20their%20desks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20employers%2C%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20the%20at-home%20crowd%20might%20be%20acceptable%2C%20Ogawa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20might%20not%20be%20looking%20to%20retain%20folks%20who%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-level-job-seekers-quit-over-return-to-office-requirement-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715677981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e0d9c66080194819fb54ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-level-job-seekers-quit-over-return-to-office-requirement-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20a%20third%20of%20p