%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fcha-hak-yeon-in-talks-to-join-jung-kyung-ho-and-seol-in-ah-in-upcoming-drama-labor-attorney-noh-moo-jin%2Farticleshow%2F110112677.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat%20He%20Has%20Done%20For%20Yoga%20Is%20Good%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20Ramdev%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Blot%20of%20influence%26quot%3B%20and%20must%20use%20it%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20right%20way%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%20while%20hearing%20the%20misleading%20ads%20case%20against%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20and%20its%20founders%20Ramdev%20and%20Balakrishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20today's%20proceedings%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Balbir%20Singh%20told%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%20that%20Patanjali%20has%20written%20to%20TV%20channels%20where%20its%20ads%20are%20still%20running%20and%20stopped%20sale%20of%20the%20products%20in%20question.%20The%20court%20asked%20Patanjali%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20about%20the%20stocks%20of%20these%20products.%20The%20court%20also%20accepted%20Ramdev%20and%20Balakrishna's%20request%20to%20dispense%20with%20their%20presence%20in%20court%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBaba%20Ramdev%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20influence%2C%20use%20it%20in%20the%20right%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%20When%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20mentioned%20that%20Ramdev%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20yoga%2C%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20he%20has%20done%20for%20yoga%20is%20good%2C%20but%20Patanjali%20products%20is%20another%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20reserved%20orders%20on%20the%20contempt%20case%20against%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna.%20The%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20next%20on%20July%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20this%20matter%20is%20about%20ensuring%20the%20public%20is%20well-informed.%20%26quot%3BPublic%20is%20cognisant%2C%20if%20they%20have%20choices%2C%20they%20make%20well-informed%20choices%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20relates%20to%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association's%20petition%20against%20Patanjali%20and%20its%20founders%20for%20misleading%20ads%20that%20claim%20its%20products%20can%20cure%20health%20conditions%20such%20as%20high%20blood%20pressure%20and%20diabetes.%20Hearing%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20warned%20Patanjali%20last%20year.%20When%20the%20ads%20did%20not%20stop%2C%20the%20court%20issued%20a%20contempt%20notice%20and%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Patanjali%20promoters.%20It%20rejected%20multiple%20sets%20of%20ideologies%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20heartfelt%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20a%20lip%20service%26quot%3B.%20Under%20fire%2C%20Patanjali%20put%20out%20an%20apology%20in%20newspapers.%20This%20did%20not%20convince%20the%20court%20and%20it%20asked%20if%20the%20size%20of%20the%20apology%20was%20similar%20to%20full-page%20advertisements%20of%20its%20products.%20Ramdev%20and%20Balakrishna%20then%20issued%20fresh%20apologies%2C%20displayed%20prominently%20in%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715677200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fad6iitio_ramdev-ani-650-_650x400_10_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpatanjali-ramdev-ramdev-has-influence-must-use-it-in-right-way-supreme-court-in-ads-case-5660331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Blot%20of%20influence%26quot%3B%20and%20must%20use%20it%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20right%20way%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%20while%20hearing%20the%20misleading%20ads%20case%20against%20Patanjali%20