20or%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-valuation-mrbeast-how-much-worth-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20type%20of%20ad%20that%20internet%20users%20see%2C%20the%20frequency%20with%20which%20the%20ad%20is%20served%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20placement%20of%20a%20given%20Google%20Ad%20all%20depend%20on%20the%20advertiser's%20spend%20and%20the%20online%20behavior%20of%20the%20people%20who%20end%20up%20seeing%20it.%20This%20confluence%20helps%20make%20Google%20Ads%20a%20good%20investment%20for%20the%20advertiser%20and%20%E2%80%94%20often%2C%20anyway%20%E2%80%94%20a%20relevant%20experience%20for%20the%20people%20who%20see%20and%20may%20click%20on%20the%20ads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20as%20Google%20AdWords%20in%202000%2C%20the%20platform's%20name%20switched%20to%20Google%20Ads%20in%202018%20and%20it's%20diversified%20in%20many%20ways%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22912649ae-a308-4cae-b91e-e16d2313cc0f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%20Ads%3A%20The%20price%20and%20the%20potential%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20worried-looking%20small%20business%20owner%20sitting%20in%20his%20store%20stares%20at%20his%20laptop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66267b6e83c8ec6e153084c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUsing%20Google%20Ads%20can%20be%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20you%20pay%20per%20click%2C%20but%20you%20can%20set%20a%20maximum%20budget%20for%20your%20ad.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20Google%20Ads%20so%20expensive%3F%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20questions%20associated%20with%20Google%20Ads.%20The%20simple%20answer%20is%20because%20it's%20effective%20and%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20different%20businesses%2C%20brands%2C%20and%20individuals%20vying%20for%20visibility%20on%20Google%2C%20the%20higher-ranking%20search%20terms%20get%20more%20and%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20per%20click%20is%20around%20%243.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20for%20search%20terms%20with%20very%20little%20competition%2C%20you%20may%20pay%20mere%20pennies%20for%20each%20ad%20click.%20Other%20ads%20may%20cost%20their%20creators%20%2450%20or%20more%20for%20every%20single%20click.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20for%20someone%20clicking%20on%20an%20image%2C%20video%2C%20or%20text%20ad%20that%20will%20lead%20them%20to%20your%20site%2C%20feed%2C%20or%20product%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20no%20guarantee%20they'll%20take%20further%20action%20that%20will%20be%20profitable%20to%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20remember%2C%20you%20don't%20pay%20anything%20until%20that%20click%20happens.%20you'll%20never%20be%20hit%20with%20a%20surprise%20expense%20that's%20beyond%20your%20budget%20because%20you%20set%20a%20maximum%20spend%20for%20each%20ad.%20Plus%2C%20you%20know%20that%20every%20time%20you%20do%20pay%20for%20your%20Google%20ad%2C%20it's%20because%20someone%20took%20the%20exact%20action%20you%20hoped%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20to%20address%20another%20common%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20Google%20Ads%20free%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20answer%20is%20a%20resounding%20no.%20Unlike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fadd-business-to-google%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Business%20Profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20free%20service%20to%20let%20business%20owners%20control%20how%20their%20business%20appears%20in%20Google%20search%20results%2C%20Google%20Ads%20will%20cost%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20Google%20Ads%20worth%20it%2C%20given%20the%20potentially%20high%20cost%20per%20click%3F%20If%20used%20well%2C%20absolutely%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244420ee3-2888-4db2-93c0-7eecb0396ccb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifferent%20types%20of%20Google%20Ads%20serve%20different%20purposes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20primary%20types%20of%20Google%20Ads%3A%20Search%20ads%2C%20which%20appear%20above%20and%20among%20the%20organic%20search%20results%3B%20video%20ads%2C%20which%20run%20before%20or%20during%20YouTube%20videos%3B%20Google%20Display%20Ads%2C%20which%20are%20embedded%20among%20the%20content%20of%20websites%3B%20Google%20Shopping%20Ads%2C%20which%20pop%20up%20with%20images%2C%20brief%20text%2C%20and%20pricing%20info%20when%20someone%20searches%20for%20a%20specific%20product%20or%20product%20category%3B%20and%20Google%20app%20ads%2C%20which%20are%20app-related%20and%20show%20up%20in%20the%20Google%20Play%20store%2C%20among%20search%20results%2C%20and%20on%20YouTube%20and%20other%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20also%20offers%20more%20specialized%20ad%20campaigns%2C%20such%20as%20Performance%20Max%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20AI%20optimization%20to%20help%20your%20ads%20perform%20as%20well%20as%20possible.%20In%20February%202024%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-ai-model-says-company-has-virtual-monopoly-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Gemini%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20model%20will%20be%20incorporated%20into%20Performance%20Max%20to%20help%20advertisers%20build%20more%20effective%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incorporation%20of%20AI%20into%20Google%20Ads%20has%20sparked%20concerns%20within%20Google%20and%20the%20advertising%20industry%20that%20automation%20will%20replace%20workers.%20Late%20in%202023%2C%20numerous%20media%20outlets%20reported%20that%20Google%20Ads%20would%20undergo%20a%20restructuring%2C%20to%20include%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-layoffs-more-employees-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20affected%20Waze%2C%20the%20company's%20traffic%20and%20navigation%20app%2C%20in%202023%20when%20its%20advertising%20system%20merged%20with%20Google%20Ads%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295956aec-b09c-4eed-b96b-f1f63319d778%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20make%20money%20with%20Google%20ads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20at%20a%20desk%20works%20on%20his%20laptop%20with%20budget%20documents%20nearby.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662683dc83c8ec6e1530904f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20make%20money%20with%20Google%20Ads%2C%20but%20the%20service%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20business%20owners%20are%20thoughtful%20and%20deliberate%20about%20their%20ads.%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20Google%20ads%20offer%20advertisers%20the%20ability%20to%20tailor%20the%20ad%20to%20users.%20Said%20action%20can%20be%20a%20purchase%2C%20a%20subscription%2C%20a%20share%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20targeting%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20selecting%20user%20traits%20like%20age%2C%20location%2C%20and%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20ad%20type%20you%20choose%20should%20be%20well-reasoned%3A%20if%20you're%20selling%20gardening%20tools%2C%20a%20search%20or%20shopping%20ad%20probably%20makes%20the%20most%20sense.%20But%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20spread%20awareness%20of%20a%20new%20VR%20video%20game%2C%20then%20an%20ad%20on%20YouTube%20is%20a%20savvy%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20care%20with%20which%20you%20choose%20terms%20in%20a%20Google%20ad%20will%20help%20the%20advertisement%20perform%20well%2C%20although%20it's%20more%20expensive%20when%20you%20place%20high-ranking%20terms%20in%20your%20ad.%20That's%20because%20Google's%20algorithms%20deem%20advertisements%20with%20well-chosen%20and%20well-used%20keywords%20%E2%80%94%20words%20that%20read%20organically%20rather%2