es-last-chance-to-meet-her-dying-husband-as-air-india-express-cancels-flight%2Farticleshow%2F110111273.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20tragic%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20Amrita%2C%20a%20woman%20whose%20husband%20was%20in%20a%20critical%20condition%20in%20an%20Oman%20hospital's%20ICU%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20see%20him%20one%20last%20time%20before%20his%20passing%20due%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20her%20Air%20India%20Express%20flight%20last%20week.%20Despite%20booking%20tickets%20for%20May%208%20to%20visit%20her%20husband%20in%20Muscat%2C%20Amrita%20was%20informed%20upon%20reaching%20the%20airport%20that%20her%20flight%20had%20been%20cancelled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Dietary%20Guidelines%20In%20India%20Have%20Advised%20Avoiding%20Protein%20Supplements%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProtein%20supplements%2C%20which%20come%20with%20added%20sugars%20and%20additives%2C%20may%20harm%20the%20kidneys%20and%20bones%20and%20are%20not%20required%20for%20healthy%20people%2C%20said%20experts%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20even%20as%20the%20ICMR-NIN's%20new%20dietary%20guidelines%20also%20advise%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20and%20National%20Institute%20of%20Nutrition%20(ICMR-NIN)%2C%20last%20week%2C%20released%2017%20dietary%20guidelines%20to%20prevent%20nutrient%20deficiencies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20address%20the%20rising%20risk%20of%20obesity%2C%20diabetes%2C%20and%20cardiovascular%20diseases%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20guidelines%2C%20which%20include%20evidence-based%20food%20and%20lifestyle-related%20recommendations%2C%20called%20out%20against%20the%20need%20for%20protein%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20a%20healthy%20and%20proper%20diet%20is%20enough%20to%20fulfil%20the%20protein%20requirements%20of%20all%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20new%20guidelines%2C%20the%20recommendation%20for%20protein%20is%200.83g%2Fkg%2Fday%2C%20and%20the%20estimated%20average%20intake%20is%200.66%20g%2Fkg%2Fday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20increased%20knowledge%20and%20information%20about%20micronutrients%20and%20their%20importance%20in%20a%20balanced%20diet%2C%20people%20have%20resorted%20to%20protein%20powder%2C%20protein%20supplements%2C%20among%20other%20artificial%20nutritional%20supplements%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20N%20Vijayshree%2C%20Head%20and%20Chief%20Dietician%20of%20MGM%20Healthcare%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20protein%20powders%20are%20usually%20made%20with%20eggs%2C%20milk%2C%20whey%2C%20or%20plant%20sources%20such%20as%20soy%2C%20peas%2C%20or%20rice%2C%20sometimes%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20these%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20supplements%2C%20with%20added%20sugars%20and%20additives%2C%20defeat%20the%20purpose%20of%20having%20a%20balanced%20diet%2C%20causing%20severe%20or%20more%20damage%20to%20our%20kidneys%20and%20bone%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVani%20Krishna%2C%20Chief%20Nutritionist%2C%20at%20Manipal%20Hospital%20Varthur%2C%20told%20IANS%20that%20protein%20intake%20can%20be%20achieved%20by%20adding%20legumes%2C%20pulses%2C%20nuts%2C%20seeds%2C%20eggs%2C%20poultry%2C%20fish%2C%20etc%20with%20a%20balanced%20diet%20for%20all%20age%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20individual's%20protein%20intake%20has%20to%20be%20assessed%20and%20checked%20by%20a%20qualified%20clinical%20nutritionist%20before%20administering%20any%20kind%20of%20protein%20powders%2Fsupplements.%20For%20obtaining%20good%20quality%20protein%2C%20a%20combination%20of%20cereals%20with%20pulses%20in%20the%20ratio%20of%203%3A1%20will%20help%20to%20meet%20the%20amino%20acids%20needed%20in%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Vani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Vijayshree%20also%20advised%20physical%20activity%20to%20use%20the%20protein%20consumed%20and%20avoid%20muscle%20loss%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20adequate%20amount%20of%20carbs%20and%20fats%20for%20the%20effective%20utilisation%20of%20the%20consumed%20protein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20balanced%20diet%20must%20meet%20the%20need%20for%2020%20essential%20amino%20acids%20required%20for%20bodily%20functions.%20To%20obtain%20some%20of%20these%20amino%20acids%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20synthesised%20in%20our%20body%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20consume%20diverse%20food%20groups%20like%20carbohydrates%2C%20fats%2C%20and%20protein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProtein%20supplements%20are%20not%20recommended%20for%20normal%2C%20healthy%20people.%20Critically%20ill%2C%20hospitalised%20patients%20may%20require%20protein%20supplements%2C%20which%20should%20be%20recommended%20and%20monitored%20by%20clinical%20professionals%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Vijayshree%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715675100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fagi66hq4_protein-supplements-protein-shake-generic-unsplash_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-new-dietary-guidelines-in-india-have-advised-avoiding-protein-supplements-5659689%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20and%20National%20Institute%20of%20Nutrition%2C%20last%20week%2C%20released%2017%20dietary%20guidelines%20to%20prevent%20nutrient%20deficiencies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20address%20the%20rising%20risk%20of%20obesity%2C%20diabetes%2C%20and%20cardiovascular%20diseases%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-new-dietary-guidelines-in-india-have-advised-avoiding-protein-supplements-5659689%2