%20big%20jump%20from%20the%203.72%20lakh%20winning%20margin%20five%20years%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202014%20election%20Varanasi%20saw%20a%20high-profile%20clash%20between%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20gathered%20a%20little%20over%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20on%20his%20debut%20in%20the%20BJP%20fortress.%20This%20time%20around%20(on%20paper)%20the%20PM's%20rival%20is%20the%20Congress'%20Ajay%20Rai.%20Mr%20Rai%20contested%20in%202019%20and%20got%201.52%20lakh%20votes%2C%20and%20an%20improved%20vote%20share%20of%207.04%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindus%20make%20up%20around%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20Varanasi's%20demographic.%20Muslims%20make%20up%2020%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%20belong%20to%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20only%200.7%20are%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20The%20rural-urban%20split%20of%20the%20population%20is%2065%20to%2035%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20also%20bidding%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20has%20set%20itself%20a%20target%20of%20370%2B%20seats%20(400%2B%20with%20its%20allies)%2C%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20led%20the%20party's%20charge%2C%20with%20strident%20attacks%20on%20the%20Congress-led%20opposition%2C%20i%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnotice-to-bjp-congress-over-poll-violation-complaints-against-pm-modi-rahul-gandhi-5519133%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Encluding%20controversial%20references%20to%20Muslims%20that%20were%20widely%20condemned%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20drew%20cautious%20reprimands%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20The%20poll%20panel%20sent%20notices%20to%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20and%2C%20responding%20to%20complaints%20filed%20by%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20also%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20March%2C%20while%20announcing%20the%20dates%20of%20the%20