y%208%20to%20see%20her%20husband%20in%20Muscat%2C%20but%20on%20reaching%20the%20airport%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20she%20was%20told%20that%20the%20flight%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20protest%20at%20the%20airport%20earned%20her%20a%20ticket%20for%20the%20next%20day%20on%20another%20Air%20India%20Express%20flight%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20that%20too%20was%20cancelled%20and%20she%20had%20to%20abandon%20her%20travel%20plans%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20news%20of%20her%20husband's%20death%20reached%20her%20from%20Oman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20unfair%20that%20she%20could%20not%20see%20him%20for%20one%20last%20time.%20We%20begged%20the%20airline%20to%20accommodate%20us%20on%20some%20other%20flight%20so%20that%20we%20could%20see%20him%20for%20one%20last%20time.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Amrita's%20mother%20told%20a%20TV%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20Amrita's%20husband%20had%20said%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20see%20his%20wife%20and%20kids%20and%20that%20is%20why%20they%20had%20booked%20tickets%20to%20go%20see%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmrita%2C%20who%20later%20spoke%20to%20reporters%2C%20said%20that%20after%20the%20second%20flight%20was%20also%20cancelled%2C%20the%20airline%20told%20her%20nothing%20could%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%20their%20flights%20for%20the%20next%20four%20days%20were%20full%20and%20they%20cannot%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%20was%20hospitalised%20following%20a%20massive%20heart%20attack.%20%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20to%20him%20over%20the%20phone.%20Told%20him%20I%20will%20try%20to%20reach%20there%20if%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20Express%20had%20cancelled%20%26quot%3Bscores%20of%20flights%26quot%3B%20last%20week%20due%20to%20a%20shortage