u%20can't%20vent%20your%20feelings%20against%20the%20court%20in%20the%20press%20like%20this.%20What%20made%20you%20go%20suddenly%20like%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Asokan%20offered%20an%20unconditional%20apology.%20Justice%20Kohli%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWhether%20we%20should%20accept%20your%20statements%20after%20such%20damaging%20statements%2C%20you%20are%20the%20one%20who%20dragged%20the%20other%20side%20to%20the%20court%2C%20saying%20they%20are%20denigrating%20you%2C%20but%20when%20you%20are%20put%20to%20test...%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20added%20that%20it%20is%20not%20happy%20with%20his%20affidavit.%20Questioning%20why%20he%20did%20not%20issue%20a%20public%20apology%2C%20the%20court%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20written%20in%20black%20and%20white%2C%20why%20did%20you%20not%20make%20amends%20if%20you%20truly%20wanted%20to%20apologise%3F%20What%20did%20you%20do%20to%20redeem%20yourself%20after%20the%20interview%3F%20Tell%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20first%20one%20to%20uphold%20the%20freedom%20of%20free%20speech.%20But%20there%20are%20times%20when%20there%20should%20be%20self-restraint.%20As%20IMA%20President%2C%20you%20should%20have%20had%20self-restraint.%20That's%20the%20point!%20We%20didn't%20see%20that%20in%20your%20interviews%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kohli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDr%20Asokan%2C%20you%20are%20also%20a%20citizen%20of%20this%20country.%20The%20amount%20of%20criticism%20judges%20face%2C%20why%20don't%20they%20react%3F%20Because%20personally%20we%20don't%20have%20much%20of%20an%20ego%2C%20we%20are%20magnanimous.%20We%20are%20entitled%20to%20take%20action%2C%20but%20very%20rarely%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Amanullah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20judges%20use%20their%20discretion%20with%20some%20sense%20of%20responsibility.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20you%20go%20to%20town%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20comments.%20You%20cannot%20just%20sit%20on%20a%20couch%20and%20say%20anything%20about%20the%20court.%20What%20would%20you%20have%20done%20if%20other%20side%20made%20this%20kind%20of%20comments!%20You%20would%20have%20come%20running%20to%20this%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0The%20court%20said%20it%20is%20not%20convinced%20by%20the%20affidavit%20submitted%20by%20the%20IMA%20president%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Btoo%20little%2C%20too%20late%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Senior%20Advocate%20PS%20Patwalia%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20IMA%20president%2C%20urged%20the%20court%20for%20relief%2C%20Justice%20Kohli%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20sauce%20for%20the%20goose%2C%20is%20sauce%20for%20the%20gander%20...%20You%20can't%20say%20anything%20and%20everything%20and%20then%20meekly%20say%20he%20fell%20in%20error.%20Are%20you%20saying%20he%20fell%20into%20some%20trap%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20few%20weeks%20have%20seen%20the%20tables%20turn%20in%20the%20case%20against%20Patanjali.%20Earlier%2C%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20were%20admonished%20by%20the%20court%20over%20Patanjali's%20ads%20that%20claimed%20to%20cure%20health%20conditions%20such%20as%20high%20blood%20pressure%20and%20diabetes.%20The%20court%20also%20rejected%20multiple%20apologies%20by%20the%20two.%20However%2C%20the%20IMA%20president's%20interview%20has%20put%20the%20petitioner%20medical%20body%20in%20a%20spot%20and%20the%20court%20has%20pulled%20him%20up.%20The%20matter%20has%20been%20posted%20for%20next%20hearing%20on%20July%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715671080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2Fvoni7s98_supreme-court-new_650x400_12_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-patanjali-case-should-have-had-self-restraint-supreme-court-rebukes-medical-body-chief-5659647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coming%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20president%2