d%20they%20make%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillet-based%20ice%20cream%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20four%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20to%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabu%20(45)%2C%20a%20hotelier%20with%20over%2025%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20field%2C%20crossed%20paths%20with%20Shashidhar%20(37)%2C%20a%20food%20scientist%2C%20through%20work.%20They%20became%20friends%20over%20their%20common%20love%20for%20food%20and%20nutrition.%20Arun%20(33)%2C%20a%20marketing%20professional%20working%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20was%20Prabu%E2%80%99s%20neighbour%20in%20Trichy%2C%20while%20Bhargav%20(39)%20is%20a%20fintech%20expert%20working%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20Shashidhar%E2%80%99s%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Siri%20ice-creams%20are%20millet-based%20and%20vegan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349382%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESiri%20ice-creams%20are%20millet-based%20and%20vegan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20work%20took%20them%20to%20different%20continents%2C%20they%20all%20wanted%20to%20eventually%20come%20back%20to%20be%20with%20their%20ageing%20parents.%20Their%20families%20owned%20farmlands%20on%20which%20they%20grew%20paddy%2C%20which%20was%20becoming%20a%20problem%20due%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20green%20revolution%2C%20our%20grandparents%20were%20growing%20millets%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%2C%20ragi%2C%20and%20bajra%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20their%20farms%2C%20which%20require%20less%20water%20and%20are%20resilient%20to%20climate%20change.%20The%20advent%20of%20the%20green%20revolution%20caused%20a%20shift%20to%20paddy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shashidhar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabu%20chimes%20in%2C%20as%20Arun%20and%20his%20family%20too%2C%20share%20a%20similar%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20no%20secret%20that%20farmers%20in%20the%20delta%20districts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20including%20Trichy%2C%20have%20experienced%20years%20of%20poor%20paddy%20yields%20due%20to%20insufficient%20water%20for%20irrigation%2C%20forcing%20many%20to%20seek%20alternative%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20of%20discussion%20before%20they%20quit%20their%20jobs%20led%20them%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20cultivating%20millets%20on%20their%20existing%20land%20in%20Trichy%20and%20Hyderabad.%20Shashidhar%20even%20purchased%20an%20additional%2040%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20started%20growing%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20ragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20seasonal%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20growing%20millets%20was%20one%20part%20of%20the%20vision%2C%20the%20other%20part%20was%20drawn%20from%20their%20experiences.%20They%20noticed%20a%20shift%20towards%20healthy%2C%20vegan%20food%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20dietary%20requirements%20were%20changing.%20There%20was%20an%20increasing%20demand%20for%20vegan%2C%20non-dairy%20alternatives%2C%20as%20more%20people%20are%20getting%20lactose%20intolerant.%20In%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20people%20were%20asking%20for%20almond%20and%20oats%20milk%2C%20which%20made%20us%20wonder%20about%20an%20Indian%2C%20vegan%20alternative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prabu%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20years%20after%20starting%20Siri%20Millets%2C%20they%20launched%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cookies%2C%20vermicelli%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Erava.%3C%2Fem%3E%20They%20piloted%20these%20value-added%20products%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Gujarat%20by%20providing%20them%20to%20students%20in%20government%20schools%20for%2045%20days%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20founders%20conduct%20awareness%20programs%20in%20schools%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691-300x212.jpeg%20300w%2C%20