0months%2C%20they%20found%20that%20the%20major%20millets%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%2C%20bajra%2C%20ragi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20foxtail%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20produced%20good%20results.%20They%20then%20experimented%20with%20different%20sweeteners%20and%20fruits%2C%20and%20developed%20these%20ice-creams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20made-in-India%20vegan%20ice-cream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20six%20months%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20they%20finally%20started%20testing.%20They%20offered%20samples%20to%20neighbours%20and%20gated%20communities%20in%20Trichy.%20The%20overall%20feedback%20was%20positive%20with%20fresh%20fruit%20ice-creams%20emerging%20a%20clear%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1043tAKbEp%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1043tAKbEp%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1043tAKbEp%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20SIRI%20House%20of%20Vegan%20Ice%20Creams%20(%40sirimillets_veganicecreams)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20worked%20on%20the%20feedback%20for%20two%20more%20months%20and%20then%20launched%20their%20first%20%E2%80%98Siri%20%E2%80%93%20House%20of%20Vegan%20Ice%20Creams%E2%80%99%20store%20in%20Trichy%20in%202020.%20The%20flavours%20they%20offer%20range%20from%20vanilla%2C%20chocolate%2C%20mango%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20and%20jamun%2C%20to%20red%20guava%2C%20dates%2C%20banana%2C%20musk%20melon%2C%20strawberry%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20coconut%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20vegan%20ice%20creams%2C%20millet%20milk%20is%20subtle%20and%20does%20not%20dominate%20other%20flavours.%20We%20use%20different%20sweeteners%20in%20different%20ice%20creams%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20fruits%20being%20used.%20For%20example%2C%20jaggery%20works%20well%20with%20some%20fruits%2C%20while%20palm%20sugar%20works%20better%20with%20some.%20It%20also%20varies%20depending%20on%20the%20millet%20being%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Prabu%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20also%20sell%20shakes%2C%20waffles%2C%20brownies%2C%20and%20other%20products%20in%20their%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20scoop%20of%20ice%20cream%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2030%2C%20and%20a%20one-litre%20pack%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%20800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20factory%20in%20Trichy%20has%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349601%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20factory%20in%20Trichy%20has%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20that%2C%20they%20also%20realised%20that%20these%20nutritious%20ice%20creams%20are%20a%20good%20way%20to%20introduce%20children%20to%20millets%20and%20get%20them%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20this%20traditional%20Indian%20grain!%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20think%20of%20millets%20as%20a%20punishment.%20Research%20shows%20that%20kids%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267083%2Fpapacream-woman-entrepreneur-vegan-ice-cream-engineer-quits-job-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eice%20creams%20and%20shakes%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%2C%20this%20would%20be%20a%20good%20mode%20to%20introduce%20them%20to%20these%20powerhouses%20of%20nutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20millets%20are%20procured%20from%20their%20own%20farms%2C%20and%20other%20farmers%20in%20Theni%2C%20Dharmapuri%2C%20and%20Krishnagiri%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20is%20entirely%20self-funded%2C%20with%20each%20of%20the%20four%20founders%20investing%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20their%20savings%20into%20realising%20their%20dream.%20Their%20most%20significant%20hurdle%20post-launch%20has%20been%20the%20widespread%20lack%20of%20awareness%20surrounding%20millets.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20diligently%20engaged%20in%20consumer%20education%20initiatives%2C%20conducting%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20create%20customer%20awareness.%20We%20started%20visiting%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20educate%20the%20youth%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20nutritious%20eating%20habits.%20We%20believe%20that%20knowledge%20is%20the%20key%20to%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20take%20students%20on%20a%20factory%20tour%20to%20show%20them%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20In%202023%2C%20they%20established%20a%20factory%20in%20Trichy%2C%20with%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20opened%20outlets%20in%20Hyderabad%20near%20the%20Statue%20of%20Equality%20and%20one%20in%20Rajahmundry.%20They%20are%20poised%20to%20launch%2010%20to%2012%20more%20outlets%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20community%20engagement%20is%20equally%20important.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20treasures%20of%20our%20ancestors%2C%20adapted%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20is%20seeing%20an%20increasing%20shift%20towards%20millets%2C%20this%20is%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20include%20them%20in%20our%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Prabu%20Venugopal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715180752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F%40Siri-Millet-Ice-Creams-52-of-64-min-1715319230.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prabu%20Venugopal%2C%20Shashidhar%2C%20Arun%20Prakash%2C%20and%20Bhargav%20left%20their%20comfortable%20careers%20to%20introduce%20a%20healthy%2C%20vegan%20ice%20cream%20alterna