back%20home%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20household%20that%20witnessed%20a%20confluence%20of%20culture%20as%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20Punjabi%20descent%20and%20love%20for%20%3Cem%3Erajma%20chawal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(red%20kidney%20beans%20in%20a%20thick%20gravy%20served%20with%20rice)%20blended%20with%20their%20occasional%20preference%20for%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20crepe%20made%20with%20fermented%20batter)%20and%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20savoury%20condiment).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20powerhouse%20of%20flavour%20that%20Saigal%20has%20been%20bringing%20to%20the%20MasterChef%20table%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20season.%20And%20her%20culinary%20prowess%20has%20been%20winning%20both%20palettes%20and%20hearts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20settles%20down%20for%20a%20t%C3%AAte-%C3%A0-t%C3%AAte%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20where%20she%20shares%20the%20reciprocal%20relationship%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20always%20shared%20with%20food%2C%20traces%20her%20steps%20back%20to%20the%20biggest%20influences%20in%20her%20life%2C%20and%20elaborates%20on%20how%20the%20dots%20connected%20to%20lead%20her%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292787%2Fmasterchef-australia-sandeep-pandit-revives-traditional-kashmiri-pandit-recipes-indian-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld%E2%80%99s%20most%20coveted%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99d%20say%20my%20paternal%20grandfather%20impacted%20my%20love%20for%20food%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20His%20ideas%20were%20almost%20like%20mind-benders%20for%20me.%20They%20caused%20me%20to%20think%20beyond%20the%20obvious.%E2%80%9D%20An%20anecdote%20that%20sums%20up%20her%20%3Cem%3Edarji%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20out-of-the-box%20thinking%20is%20when%20on%20a%20shopping%20spree%20he%20picked%20up%20a%20bottle%20of%20ketchup%2C%20took%20a%20good%20look%20at%20the%20ingredients%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20we%20can%20make%20this%20at%20home!%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20his%20word%2C%20he%20spent%20the%20next%20many%20hours%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20experimenting%20to%20get%20the%20flavours%20right.%20And%20the%20result%20was%20pretty%20good%2C%20Saigal%20affirms.%20When%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20prodding%20her%20to%20think%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20the%20ordinary%2C%20he%20was%20researching%20recipes%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%20And%20as%20grandfather%20and%20granddaughter%20sat%20down%20to%20dissect%20these%2C%20fascination%20flooded%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20was%20amazed%20at%20his%20thirst%20for%20knowledge%20and%20his%20hunger%20made%20me%20hungry%20to%20learn%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reminisces.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229381%2Fzero-waste-how-to-cook-cooking-tips-traditional-indian-food-using-leftovers-mother-grandmother-recipes-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAstounding%20cooking%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20run%20in%20the%20family%20DNA%3B%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20stories%20reveal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20of%20restaurants%20in%20India%20helmed%20by%20her%20extended%20family%20are%20a%20testament%20to%20this%20%E2%80%94%20The%20Great%20Punjab%20restaurant%2C%20Hotel%20Diplomat%20(adjacent%20to%20the%20iconic%20Taj%20Palace%20Hotel)%2C%20Jashan%20restaurant%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Sher-e-Punjab%20in%20Pune.%20Through%20these%20ventures%2C%20the%20family%20has%20been%20delighting%20generations%20with%20their%20food%20and%20flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20performance%20in%20the%20MasterChef%20kitchen%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20this.%20But%20the%20jour