n%2C%20she%20opted%20for%20Urban%20Planning%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20way%20villages%20work.%20%E2%80%9CI%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20rural%20lifestyle.%20The%20city%20life%20is%20good%20but%20if%20I%20was%20given%20a%20choice%2C%20I%20would%20have%20lived%20in%20a%20smaller%20city%20or%20farming%20in%20a%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20love%20was%20nurtured%20over%20time%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20study%20urban%20farming%20and%20nutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aditi%20Mali%20of%20Mali%20Greens.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349306%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAditi%20Mali%20of%20Mali%20Greens.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20was%20a%20commerce%20student%20in%20school%20and%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20could%20not%20do%20a%20masters%20in%20farming.%20I%20was%20adamant%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20urban%20farming%20which%20is%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20look%20for%20colleges%20outside%20India.%20I%20found%20one%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20got%20admitted%20into%