d%20dump%20all%20the%20unsold%20sarees.%20The%20onus%20to%20sell%20these%20would%20fall%20on%20us.%20But%20with%20Deeva%2C%20we%20get%20orders%20only%20after%20the%20consumer%20has%20placed%20an%20order%2C%20and%20we%20get%20payments%20in%207%20to%2010%20days.%20Here%2C%20my%20income%20has%20also%20increased%20by%2025%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20to%20make%20Deeva%20a%20big%20brand%2C%20Ankush%20wanted%20to%20appear%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%20Even%20though%20he%20could%20not%20make%20it%20to%20season%202%2C%20he%20made%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98sharks%E2%80%99%20in%20season%203.%20The%20impact%20of%20the%20episode%20was%20so%20enormous%20that%20he%20observed%20a%20boost%20of%20six%20times%20in%20his%20business%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooted%20in%20his%20village%2C%20Ankush%20now%20aims%20to%20make%20a%20business%20of%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20enter%20into%20export%20in%20at%20least%2010%20countries%2C%20and%20open%20offline%20stores%20in%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20feel%20I%20have%20achieved%20very%20big.%20It%20was%20through%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20that%20we%20started%20getting%20meals%20three%20times%20a%20day.%20My%20parents%20worked%20hard%20so%20that%20we%20could%20wear%20decent%20clothes.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20give%20whatever%20best%20life%20I%20can%20to%20my%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20gifted%20a%20seven-seater%20car%20to%20my%20father.%20Currently%2C%20we%20are%20building%20our%20dream%20house%20with%20a%20helipad%20and%20rooftop%20swimming%20pool%20in%20Himachal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20these%20are%20materialistic%20things%2C%20having%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebada%20ghar%2C%20badi%20gaadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(big%20house%2C%20big%20car)%20are%20dreams%20of%20a%20lower-middle%20income%20family.%20In%20eight%20months%2C%20I%20will%20move%20to%20our%20new%20home%20with%20my%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Ankush%20Barjata.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714745043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-1714728877.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankush%20Barjata%20founded%20an%20online%20saree%20platform%20named%20'Deeva'%20from%20a%20small%20Himachal%20village.%20His%20journey%2C%20rooted%20in%20his%20family's%20clothing%20legacy%2C%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20vision%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20life%20for%20his%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348898%2Fsaree-startup-online-business-ankush-barjata-founded-deeva-buy-shark-tank-india-bangana-himachal%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20Rebukes%20Trader%20Joe%E2%80%99s%20For%20%E2%80%98Meritless%E2%80%99%20Trademark%20Lawsuit%20Against%20Workers'%20Union%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20judge%20ordered%20the%20grocer%20to%20pay%20the%20union%E2%80%99s%20legal%20fees%20after%20it%20tried%20to%20claim%20the%20union%20had%20violated%20its%20trademarks.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714528502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65a2ecd0240000310027f382.jpeg%3Fcache%3DY1vCvJuNVa%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-ordered-to-pay-attorneys-fees_n_663197f4e4b0279447ac92f2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20judge%20ordered%20the%20grocer%20to%20pay%20the%20union%E2%80%99s%20legal%20fees%20after%20it%20tried%20to%20claim%20the%20union%20had%20violated%20its%20trademarks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-ordered-to-pay-attorneys-fees_n_663197f4e4b0279447